    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How much does commercial refrigerator repair cost?</h3>
        <p>Commercial diagnostic is $120, applied to the repair if approved. Most repairs run between $180 and $550. Fan motor, door gasket, coil cleaning, or drain service is toward the lower end. Compressor or refrigerant work runs higher. Full written estimate before any work begins.</p>
